               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām "Miracles of Mary" (fols. 4ra-194rb)&#xD;
I-1) ʾAkkonu bǝʾsi ... "Does not the man ..." (fols. 2r-3v l.28)&#xD;
I-2) Sǝbḥāt laki Māryām ba-ḫʷǝlqʷa kʷǝllu śǝʿǝrtǝyä ... "Glory to you, Mary, as numerous as my hair ..." (fol. 3v l.28-33)&#xD;
I-3) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 4ra-9rb)&#xD;
I-4a) Taʾāmra Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 120 miracles (fols. 12ra-171vb)&#xD;
I-4b) Taʾāmra Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 10 miracles (fols. 175ra-194rb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-4.</summary>
